works.description: After the 2009 MINI Life Ball by The Blonds and the Life Ball MINIs 2010 by celebrity fashion designers Diane von Furstenberg, Kenneth Cole and Calvin Klein Collection’s Francisco Costa, we now have the Life Ball MINI 2011. Designed by Dean and Dan Caten (aka the Canadian designer duo DSQUARED²), the Life Ball MINI 2011 is a MINI Cooper S that has been refashioned to be armed for adventures of all kinds.
